name: node-shapelib-partial
description: Node bindings for shapelib.maptools.org's shapefile inplementation
readme: Node bindings for [shapelib.maptools.org](http://shapelib.maptools.org/)'s implementation of the [ESRI](http://www.esri.com/) shapefile specification with [libuv](http://nikhilm.github.io/uvbook/index.html) for async file access and decode.
